    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.1.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Outlining the scheme of processing inventory into finished products/services. This includes the use of raw materials, machinery, skill sets, and knowledge to create new offerings.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10221 .

ex:PCF_19551 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define standard operating procedures""" ;
    ex:pcfID "19551" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.1.8" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Establishing or prescribing methods to be followed routinely for the performance of designated operations or in designated situations. This may include step-by-step instructions to help workers carry out complex routine operations. The goal is to improve efficiency, quality, and uniformity of performance, while reducing miscommunication, failure, or rework.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10221 .

ex:PCF_14194 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define production workplace layout and infrastructure""" ;
    ex:pcfID "14194" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.1.9" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining the floor plans for the processing facility that is meant for delivering finished products/services. Identify the totality of infrastructure needed for using this space in the manufacturing process, including machinery, factory floors, offices, and furniture.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10221 .

ex:PCF_10222 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage demand for products""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10222" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Forecasting demand for products using secondary research and customer feedback. Refine these forecasts. Inspect the approach used in creating forecasts, and determine its accuracy.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10215 .

ex:PCF_10235 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop baseline demand forecasts""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10235" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Identify the bedrock levels of market demand anticipated for the organization's products/services. Estimate future demand for product and services using historical data, analysis of the market environment and any externalities, etc. to create ex ante approximations.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10222 .

ex:PCF_10236 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Collaborate demand with customers""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10236" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Working closely with the organization's customers to understand their drives and behavior, with the objective of estimating future demand. Reach out to customers through various means to understand their behavior patterns, usage elasticity, and degree of variability--and ultimately determine demand for each offering.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10222 .

ex:PCF_10237 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop demand consensus forecast""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10237" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Arriving at a consensus over the forecasted levels of demand for products/services. Consensus is achieved by juxtaposing decisions developed in the baseline forecast with those reached at by collaborating with customers. Enlist senior-level decision makers of the sales and marketing functions.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10222 .

ex:PCF_10238 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Determine available to promise""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10238" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.2.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Identify the volume of products/services that may be committed for delivery to fulfill sales. Figure out the amount of stock available. Forecast its volumes.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10222 .

ex:PCF_10239 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Monitor activity against demand forecast and revise forecast""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10239" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.2.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Picking out any activity that deviates from the forecast, and adjusting it. Closely track and study the levels of demand as they emerge. Refine the consensus forecast as needed.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10222 .

ex:PCF_10240 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Evaluate and revise demand forecasting approach""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10240" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.2.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Examining the methodology used to estimate future demand. Refine it in light of current market realities and demand.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10222 .

ex:PCF_10241 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Measure demand forecast accuracy""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10241" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.2.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Calculating and inspecting the accuracy of demand forecasts. Use metrics to check the reliability of the forecasts created. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10222 .

ex:PCF_10223 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Create materials plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10223" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Developing a scheme that allows for advance planning for the availability of raw materials and spares. Start with an unconstrained plan, and refine based on supply chain realities by identifying critical materials required for production, checking material specifications, and collaborating with all vendors over the supply.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10215 .

ex:PCF_10242 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Create unconstrained plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10242" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Developing a plan for raw materials and other inventory items in order to meet market demand. Ensure the availability of all inventory items such as raw materials and spares. Create a blueprint in line with Define labor and materials policies [10230]. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10223 .

ex:PCF_10243 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Collaborate with supplier and contract manufacturers""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10243" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Collaborating with vendors and contractual manufacturers with the objective of ensuring a continual supply of raw materials and spares. Leverage long-term connections/relationships with various suppliers, and cultivate new ones. Track the activities of all vendors. Receive regular updates to prepare for any fluctuations in supply.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10223 .

ex:PCF_10244 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Identify critical materials and supplier capacity""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10244" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Identifying principal materials needed for the manufacturing process and the levels of supply that may be ensured for them. Determine the essential and crucial inventory items required for the smooth functioning of all manufacturing processes. Estimate the average, peak, and baseline capacities of various vendors and suppliers. Establish the capability of individual suppliers from the market and the vendors.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10223 .

ex:PCF_10245 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Monitor material specifications""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10245" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.3.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Observing and surveying all inventory items in order to check for the veracity of their specifications. Monitor various attributes and characteristics for respective inventory items such as density, volume, and size, as well as contextualized specifications particular to the respective materials.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10223 .

ex:PCF_10246 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Generate constrained plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10246" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.3.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Generating a bounded plan that takes stock of the actual supply chain scenario. Take stock of all information collected while creating an inventory supply plan. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10223 .

ex:PCF_14196 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define production balance and control""" ;
    ex:pcfID "14196" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.3.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Defining an equitable volume for the production of products/services that adheres to an equilibrium value, and creating a scheme of control for processing items. Create schematics for systematically planning, coordinating, and directing the manufacturing activities in line with the production balance determined.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10223 .

ex:PCF_10224 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Create and manage master production schedule""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10224" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Taking care of the master production plan. The master production includes creation and implementation of the site-level production plan, as well as management of the inventory that is currently in the production process.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10215 .

ex:PCF_20023 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Model production network to enable simulation and optimization""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20023" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.4.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Create representative logical system that provides the framework to attain strategic objectives based on resources, product volumes, and processes. Provides the general sequential flow and capacity requirement relationships among raw materials, parts, resources, finished products, and product families. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10224 .

ex:PCF_20024 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Create master production schedule""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20024" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.4.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating  the plan for internal activities such as production, inventory, and staffing. Include forecasted quantity of items to produce based on inputs from sales planning, demand planning/forecasting, and supply chain partners.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10224 .

ex:PCF_17041 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Maintain master production schedule""" ;
    ex:pcfID "17041" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.4.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Supervising and overseeing the plan for internal activities such as production, inventory, and staffing. Set the quantity of items to produce each week of a short-range planning horizon.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10224 .

ex:PCF_17042 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Plan distribution requirements""" ;
    ex:pcfID "17042" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Maintaining master data of finished products and inventory. Identify the requirements of finished products at the destination, as well as partner requirements. Calculate the consolidation at source. Manage replenishment planning. Create and administer a dispatch plan. Calculate load plans for destinations and partners. Manage the cost of supplying these products. Ensure effective utilization of capacity.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10215 .

ex:PCF_10252 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Maintain master data""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10252" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.5.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Maintaining and preserving the master data plan for distribution requirements. Create a systematic collection of facts and figures regarding the distribution of the inventories. Maintain policies, processes, and tools covering the distribution function.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17042 .

ex:PCF_10253 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Determine finished goods inventory requirements at destination""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10253" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.5.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Interact with the concerned person at the destination to validate the requirements and to avoid any miscommunication of information.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17042 .

ex:PCF_19555 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Determine product storage facility requirements""" ;
    ex:pcfID "19555" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.5.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Evaluate constraints, needs, parameters, and conditions for physical storage and retrieval of components or products for future use or shipment in a storage facility within a certain timeframe.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17042 .

ex:PCF_10254 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Calculate requirements at destination""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10254" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.5.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Interact with the concerned authority at the destination to reach a specific figure that correctly represents requirements.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17042 .

ex:PCF_10255 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Calculate consolidation at source""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10255" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.5.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining the aggregate volume of products/services consolidated at the source. Calculate the number of finished products that are ready to be delivered to the customers, particularly at one date.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17042 .

ex:PCF_10256 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage collaborative replenishment planning""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10256" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.5.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Administering the plan for collaborative replenishment of goods. Replenish inventory by creating a plan in case of faulty production.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17042 .

ex:PCF_10258 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Calculate and optimize destination dispatch plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10258" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.5.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Estimating the timing and duration of the delivery of the inventory from the source to the destination. Plan the logistic details of all the distribution routes and activities.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17042 .

ex:PCF_10259 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage dispatch plan attainment""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10259" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.5.8" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Accomplishing the dispatch plan. Strictly follow the schedule, and adjust for deviations. Coordinate with the concerned authorities at various destinations.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17042 .

ex:PCF_10260 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Calculate and optimize destination load plans""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10260" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.5.9" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Evaluating the plans for delivering loads to destinations. Create a systematic plan that specifies the load plans for every single destination.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17042 .

ex:PCF_10261 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage partner load plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10261" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.5.10" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Administering the load plan for partners. Manage the delivery, and dispatch from the source to the partners.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17042 .

ex:PCF_10262 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage cost of supply""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10262" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.5.11" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing all expenses to provide products/services in the market. Estimate the overall cost of supplying of products/inventory, including the cost distributing it through various partners and channels. Consider the cost of all the logistical processes that occur from the moment a product is ready to be dispatched to the time it reaches the destination.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17042 .

ex:PCF_10263 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage capacity utilization""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10263" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.5.12" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining the capacity utilization of the organization's production process. Realize the extent to which an enterprise uses its installed productive capacity (i.e., the relationship between output and the potential output if capacity was fully used).""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17042 .

ex:PCF_10226 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish distribution planning constraints""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10226" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Instituting the constraints for planning of distribution process. Create a plan that specifies every element in the distribution process from the blueprint of the distribution centers to how and when the inventory would reach the distribution centers.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10215 .

ex:PCF_10267 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish distribution center layout constraints""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10267" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.6.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Instituting the constraints for creating a layout for distribution center. Consider factors such as the number of customers, demand forecasting, product groups, condition of product conservation, warehousing, and transportation management.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10226 .

ex:PCF_10268 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish inventory management constraints""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10268" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.6.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining any problems that might be faced while managing inventory. Identify problems and possible issues in managing the warehousing of the raw materials, spares, and other items of inventory. Take stock of inventory needs, and determine the exact quantity of the inventory needed in the near future.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10226 .

ex:PCF_10269 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish transportation management constraints""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10269" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.6.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Identifying any potential constraints while deciding on the dispatch and delivery plan from the source to the various distribution centers. Decide how the inventory will be transported , which and how many transportation means to use, what route to take, etc.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10226 .

ex:PCF_19558 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish storage management constraints""" ;
    ex:pcfID "19558" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.6.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining potential constraints for physical storage and retrieval of components or products in a storage facility within a certain timeframe. Consider factors such as the building shape, height, capacity, door locations, lift equipment, automation, etc.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10226 .

ex:PCF_10227 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Review distribution planning policies""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10227" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Revisiting and refurbishing the policies for planning the distribution process. Asses the distribution strategies, including how the products are to be made available and sent to different distributors. Set guidelines regarding relationships between the sources and the distribution centers.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10215 .

ex:PCF_10264 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Review distribution network""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10264" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.7.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Evaluating the system that defines how the products/inventory would reach from the source (i.e., manufacturer) to the destination (i.e., retailer/distributer).""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10227 .

ex:PCF_10265 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish sourcing relationships""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10265" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.7.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Establishing relationships with transportation/distribution sources in order to ensure an effective distribution network and strategy. Screen and evaluate various sources available to pick out the best among them.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10227 .

ex:PCF_10266 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish dynamic deployment policies""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10266" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.7.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating strategic guidelines on the availability of the products at all the distribution centers. Create a dynamic network to ensure availability at all times, even in cases of defaults.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10227 .

ex:PCF_10368 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop quality standards and procedures""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10368" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.8" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Developing standards and procedures for maintaining the quality of products/services. Establish desired quality targets. Create standardized procedures for the quality. Ensure quality specifications are effectively communicated.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10215 .

ex:PCF_10371 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish quality targets""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10371" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.8.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Defining specific qualitative and quantitative target figures.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10368 .

ex:PCF_10372 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop standard testing procedures""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10372" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.8.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating standard procedures for testing the quality of products/services. Describe the steps of key processes to help ensure consistent and quality output. Define the routine instructions for performing the quality testing activity.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10368 .

ex:PCF_10373 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Communicate quality specifications""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10373" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.1.8.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Communicating the desired quality specifications to the manufacturing units, as well as the distribution centers, to avoid any misunderstanding or misinterpretation.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10368 .

ex:PCF_10216 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Procure materials and services""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10216" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating a plan for procuring materials and services. Develop strategies for sourcing materials and services. Choose the most appropriate suppliers, and develop contracts with them. Order the materials and services as per the requirements. Manage relationships with suppliers.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20022 .

ex:PCF_10277 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Provide sourcing governance and perform category management""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10277" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating strategies for procuring materials and services from various sources, and for managing and evaluating categories. Establish a procurement process that describes the approach for obtaining products and purchasing activities. Evaluate the sources. Create sourcing relationships in order to continuously improve. Re-evaluate purchasing activities. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10216 .

ex:PCF_10281 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop procurement plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10281" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating a plan for procuring materials and services. Plan what to buy, when, and from what sources. Include project requirements, the procurement team, the justification for the procurement, a timeline of events, and an explanation of the supplier selection process. Outline specific actions to start and complete purchases in order to adhere to best practices.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10277 .

ex:PCF_10282 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Clarify purchasing requirements""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10282" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Defining the purchasing requirements for materials and services. Specify the exact inventory required for the production process. Create a specific quotation for all the sources in order to avoid any duplication or overlap.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10277 .

ex:PCF_10283 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish materials management contingency plans""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10283" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.1.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Developing a strategy to deal with issues projected to arise during implementation of the inventory plan. Identify how to react to issues that arise and require changes to the inventory plan, such as a vendor failing to deliver materials on time. Collaborate with production and suppliers to prepare solutions to projected problems.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10277 .

ex:PCF_10284 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Match needs to supply capabilities""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10284" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.1.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Synchronizing the requirements of materials and services and the capacity of suppliers for providing these materials and services. Revamp the procurement needs of the company in consideration of the capabilities of the suppliers. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10277 .

ex:PCF_10285 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Analyze organization’s spend profile""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10285" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.1.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Evaluating the spend profile of the organization. Collect, cleanse, classify, and analyze the procurement data with the purpose of reducing procurement costs, improving efficiency, and monitoring compliance.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10277 .

ex:PCF_10286 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Seek opportunities to improve efficiency and value""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10286" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.1.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Seeking the most efficient sourcing and procurement opportunities.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10277 .

ex:PCF_10287 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Collaborate with suppliers to identify sourcing opportunities""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10287" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.1.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Collaborating with the suppliers of materials and services in order to determine new opportunities for sourcing. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10277 .

ex:PCF_10278 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Select suppliers and develop/maintain contracts""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10278" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Evaluating supplier options to select the most effective and efficient suppliers. Validate selected suppliers. Establish and manage supplier contracts.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10216 .

ex:PCF_10288 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Select suppliers""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10288" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Evaluating the pros and cons of various suppliers. Choose the most appropriate and cost-effective suppliers on the basis of their material quality, delivery schedules, and costs.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10278 .

ex:PCF_10289 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Certify and validate suppliers""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10289" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Validating the supply sources, and provide certification as an official supplier.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10278 .

ex:PCF_10290 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Negotiate and establish contracts""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10290" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Legally binding suppliers with the company. Negotiate contracts individually with all the suppliers that include the promised material delivery, the delivery dates and duration, etc.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10278 .

ex:PCF_10291 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage contracts""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10291" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.2.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Keeping contracts up-to-date with routine evaluation. Maintain order and discipline with the contracts in order to avoid any loss of information and mishaps.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10278 .

ex:PCF_10279 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Order materials and services""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10279" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and approving requisitions and distributing purchase orders accordingly. Hasten the procurement process to satisfy internal needs.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10216 .

ex:PCF_10292 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Process/Review requisitions""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10292" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Handling operations related to processing/reviewing the requisitions. Establish and maintain procedures for the initiation, authorization, and processing of purchase requirements to procure products/services.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10279 .

ex:PCF_10293 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Approve requisitions""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10293" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Approving requisitions for materials and services. Examine distributor-specific requests, and validate them individually.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10279 .

ex:PCF_10294 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Solicit supplier quotes""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10294" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Requesting quotes from suppliers. Use a request for quotation (RFQ) to invite suppliers into a bidding process for specific products/services.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10279 .

ex:PCF_10295 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Create/Distribute purchase orders""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10295" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.3.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and placing the orders for purchasing materials and services from suppliers. Analyze vendor quotes. Choose the most cost-effective vendors. Create vendor-specific orders. Distribute them in order to initiate the purchasing process.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10279 .

ex:PCF_10296 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Expedite orders and satisfy inquiries""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10296" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.3.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Accelerating the purchase orders in order to fulfill the internal needs (for raw materials) depicted through inquiries. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10279 .

ex:PCF_10297 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Reconcile purchase orders""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10297" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.3.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Verify that purchase orders are filled as expected: verify that items and quantities are delivered as expected, based on purchase order details and goods receipts.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10279 .

ex:PCF_10298 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Research/Resolve order exceptions""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10298" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.3.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Identifying and resolving any exceptions. Address the internal needs/inquiries for materials that cannot be procured immediately. Research inquiries that require the need of exceptional materials.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10279 .

ex:PCF_10280 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage suppliers""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10280" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Collecting and analyzing new information in order to track and rate suppliers through a supplier information management system.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10216 .

ex:PCF_10299 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Monitor/Manage supplier information""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10299" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.4.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Examining procurement and vendor performance. Report delivery timing and the quality of the materials procured through different vendors.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10280 .

ex:PCF_10300 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Prepare/Analyze procurement and supplier performance""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10300" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.4.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Assisting the production and inventory processes through the information and reports created. Use the information and metrics of the procurement and vendor performance to enhance or improve the production process.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10280 .

ex:PCF_10301 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Support inventory and production processes""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10301" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.4.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Support inventory and production processes by analyzing impact of procurement decisions and collaborating to constantly improve. (For example, perhaps minimum order requirements could be negotiated to be lower, to reduce excessive inventory and make production more flexible.)""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10280 .

ex:PCF_10302 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Monitor quality of product delivered""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10302" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.2.4.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Track the performance of the suppliers on product quality. Use this information to further improve sourcing and supplier performance. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10280 .

ex:PCF_10217 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Produce/Assemble/Test product""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10217" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Processing and delivering the finished goods manufactured by the organization. Schedule the production of products. Execute the product production activities. Perform tests to oversee and ensure quality of production. Maintain records of the production process. Track lots.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20022 .

ex:PCF_10303 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Schedule production""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10303" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Scheduling the production of final products. Generate a detailed schedule plan. Create and release production orders and lots. Schedule the planned and unplanned maintenance orders.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10217 .

ex:PCF_19563 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Model and simulate plant""" ;
    ex:pcfID "19563" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating a representation of plant facilities to optimize material flow, resource utilization, and logistics for all levels of plant planning from global production facilities, through local plants, to specific lines and enabling the comparison of production�alternatives,.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10303 .

ex:PCF_10306 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Generate line level plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10306" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Initiating the line-level plan for production. Break down the production schedule into specific lines, specifying the various objectives the production schedule.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10303 .

ex:PCF_10307 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Generate detailed schedule""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10307" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.1.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Broadening the line-level plan. Specify all the individual production processes, along with the timing and the duration to come up with a working schedule that tracks the whole process and any deviations that might occur.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10303 .

ex:PCF_10308 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Schedule production orders and create lots""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10308" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.1.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating a schedule to commence production of orders received, and creating lots to consolidate the processing. Plan when the production orders are to be initiated by commencing the operations for processing products/services. Specify which materials to produce, where to produce them, which operations will facilitate this, and on which date production is to start. Define the size of production lots, demarcating the durations of batch production.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10303 .

ex:PCF_10315 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Plan for preventive maintenance""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10315" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.1.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Scheduling planned maintenance of the production equipment.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10303 .

ex:PCF_10316 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Request unplanned maintenance""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10316" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.1.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Scheduling requested maintenance in order to address breakdowns where repairs or corrective remedies are needed immediately. Create a scheme for undertaking unplanned maintenance work on equipment/machinery that has come to be in urgent need for it. Express turnaround to redress using specialized personnel.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10303 .

ex:PCF_10309 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Release production orders and create lots""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10309" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.1.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Initiating the delivery of production orders, and creating lots. Communicate the order that specifies which material to produce, where to produce it, which operations to require, and on which date production takes place. Define how to settle the order costs. Create production lots, which is a particular production unit of an assembly that is planned and manufactured.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10303 .

ex:PCF_10304 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Produce/Assemble product""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10304" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Manufacturing the product. Convert the raw materials to develop consumer-ready products. Manage the raw materials to implement the detailed production schedule. Reproduce defectives to establish and remediate cause. Ensure production optimization and benchmark performance.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10217 .

ex:PCF_10310 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage raw material inventory""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10310" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Administering the inventory of raw materials. Manage the total cost of all component parts in stock but not yet used. Manage the cost of the direct materials (i.e., materials incorporated into the final product) and indirect materials (i.e., materials not incorporated into the final product but consumed during the production process).""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10304 .

ex:PCF_10311 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Execute detailed line schedule""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10311" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and implementing the detailed line production schedule on the ground level. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10304 .

ex:PCF_10319 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Report maintenance issues""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10319" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Recording and reporting any deviations or issues in the maintenance schedule, in the performance to the production management team, and for unplanned maintenance.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10304 .

ex:PCF_10313 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Rerun defective items""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10313" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.2.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Reproducing the items produced defectively. Assess the produced items by conducting quality and standardization tests in order to diagnose any discrepancies. Reproduce defective items.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10304 .

ex:PCF_19566 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Monitor and optimize production process""" ;
    ex:pcfID "19566" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.2.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Integrating different resources in the production process: material, personnel, equipment, robotics, etc. Includes automating and controlling the plant, performing advanced process control and real-time optimization. This activity also includes managing plant alarms and alerts.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10304 .

ex:PCF_19567 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Automate and control plant""" ;
    ex:pcfID "19567" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.2.5.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and applying technology to monitor and control the production and delivery of products and services. Automation involves a broad range of technologies.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_19566 .

ex:PCF_19568 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Perform advanced process control""" ;
    ex:pcfID "19568" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.2.5.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Including a broad range of techniques and technologies implemented within industrial process control systems that are routinely reviewed, audited, and improved, advanced process controls typically address particular performance or economic improvement opportunities. An advanced set of process control measures can be used to reduce variation and identify primary improvement options. Results of analysis are fed back into process design for incorporation into production. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_19566 .

ex:PCF_19569 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Perform real-time optimization""" ;
    ex:pcfID "19569" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.2.5.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Helping organizations increase performance and efficiency, real-time optimization is a category of closed-loop process control that aims at optimizing process performance in real time for systems. It is normally built upon model-based optimization systems and is usually large scale. Real-time optimization automatically detects errors, and can modify and eliminate both random and non-random errors, as well as analyze and monitor all systems involved.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_19566 .

ex:PCF_19570 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage plant alarms and alerts""" ;
    ex:pcfID "19570" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.2.5.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Applying human factors and instrumentation engineering and systems thinking to manage the design of an alarm or alert system to increase its usability. Typical challenges include having too many alarms in a plant, poorly designed alarms/alerts, improperly set alarm/alert points, unclear alarm/alert messages, etc. Poor alarm management is one of the leading causes of unplanned downtime.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_19566 .

ex:PCF_10314 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Assess production performance""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10314" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.2.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Analyzing and benchmarking the production process to judge its effectiveness and efficiency. Create production metrics to numerically calculate the performance of the production process.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10304 .

ex:PCF_10369 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Perform quality testing""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10369" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Executing tests to evaluate the quality of the products manufactured. Calibrate the test equipment. Conduct the actual tests. Record the results and outcomes of the quality test conducted.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10217 .

ex:PCF_10318 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Calibrate test equipment""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10318" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Regulating the equipment used for performing quality tests. Assess correspondence between the quality testing equipment and the desired quality standards. Ensure the calibration standard is more accurate than the instrument being tested.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10369 .

ex:PCF_10374 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Perform testing using the standard testing procedure""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10374" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Performing testing using calibrated equipment and in consent with the standard testing procedure, including testing time.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10369 .

ex:PCF_20956 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage quality samples""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20956" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Selecting a set of elements from a product lot to draw conclusions or make inferences about the quality of the product lot from which the sample is drawn. Sampling is frequently used because gathering data on every product produced by a company is often impossible, impractical, or too costly to collect. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10369 .

ex:PCF_10375 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Record test results""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10375" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.3.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Documenting the results and outcomes of the quality tests. Track the performance of the production process. Record/Document it to evaluate the qualitative efficiency of the production process. Use electronic devices and software in order to ensure effectiveness in recording the results and outcomes of the test.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10369 .

ex:PCF_12045 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Track and analyze non-conformance trends""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12045" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.3.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing and monitoring the occurrences of problems with a process or product. It is important that nonconformance occurrences are tracked in a standardized way so the data can easily be reviewed to assess the impact of the problem. Ongoing analysis of trends in nonconformance gives an organization the ability to make process changes to reduce the incidence and cost of nonconformances.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10369 .

ex:PCF_12046 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Perform root cause analysis""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12046" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.3.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Using a technique that helps people answer the question of why a problem occurred in the first place. It seeks to identify the origin of a problem using a specific set of steps, with associated tools, to find the primary cause of the problem to determine what happened, why, and how to reduce the likelihood that it will happen again.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10369 .

ex:PCF_10370 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Maintain production records and manage lot traceability""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10370" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Perpetuating the production records by systematically documenting and using it to ensure the effective management of lots. Determine the lot numbering system and its use. (The lot number enables tracking of the constituent parts, as well as labor and equipment records involved in the manufacturing of a product. It enables manufacturers and to perform quality control checks, calculate expiration dates, and issue corrections of their production output.)""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10217 .

ex:PCF_10376 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Determine lot numbering system""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10376" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.4.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Allotting an identification number to a particular quantity or lot of material manufactured. Assign lot numbers on the basis of specific production units, material similarity, etc. Place lot numbers on the outside of packaging.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10370 .

ex:PCF_10377 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Determine lot use""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10377" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.3.4.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Identifying the use of production lots. Define where, how, and when to use a specific production lot.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10370 .

ex:PCF_10219 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage logistics and warehousing""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10219" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Administering and overseeing all activities related to logistics and warehousing. Outline and establish a strategy for the logistics function. Plan and administer the flow of inbound materials. Administer the operational activities of warehousing and outbound transportation. Manage reverse logistics including returns and exchanges.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20022 .

ex:PCF_10338 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Provide logistics governance""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10338" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Outlining the strategy for managing logistics. Translate customer requirements logistic requirements. Create an efficient logistic network and outsourcing portions of logistics activities. Design a logistics strategy that optimizes transportation costs and schedule. Define key performance indicators.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10219 .

ex:PCF_10343 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Translate customer service requirements into logistics requirements""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10343" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining the requirements for managing the flow of things between the point of origin and the point of consumption by assessing the service requirements of the customers.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10338 .

ex:PCF_10344 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Design logistics network""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10344" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Developing a network for logistical activities. Create a network of entities through which materials and information flow, encompassing all related activities associated with the flow of transformation of products.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10338 .

ex:PCF_10345 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Communicate outsourcing needs""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10345" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.1.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Conveying outsourcing needs within the organization, with the objective of sourcing the assistance required. Define the portion of logistical activities that can be transferred to outside suppliers. Assess third-party agencies to carefully select the most appropriate agencies for outsourcing. Convey these needs to management or the appropriate authority.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10338 .

ex:PCF_10346 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop and maintain delivery service policy""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10346" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.1.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Establishing rules and regulations, as well as the terms and conditions regarding the delivery of service by the company. Develop a delivery plan that specifies what, how, when, and in which way to deliver services to the customer.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10338 .

ex:PCF_10347 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Optimize transportation schedules and costs""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10347" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.1.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Optimizing the schedule and costs of transportation services. Design a logistics strategy by strategically creating delivery routes and systems, which optimizes the overall transportation schedules and costs. Evaluate different transportation sources in order to select the most appropriate and cost-effective sources.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10338 .

ex:PCF_10348 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define key performance measures""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10348" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.1.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Establishing measures for evaluating the performance of the logistics strategy of the organization. Establish key performance indicators, including the logistics performance index, delivery in full, and delivery on time.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10338 .

ex:PCF_16905 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define reverse logistics strategy""" ;
    ex:pcfID "16905" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.1.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Establish a strategy that includes rules and regulations for the physical handling, information processing, and disposition of product and packaging returned by the buyer to the seller or an intermediary. Include return approval, transportation coordination, advance communication, product tracking, receipt, disposition of the return, and processing warranty claims in the strategy.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10338 .

ex:PCF_20936 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Plan and manage inbound material flow""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20936" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and executing a strategy for all the internal activities related to the flow/transfer of inbound materials. This process includes planning inbound material receipts, managing inbound material flow, monitoring inbound delivery performance, managing the flow of returned products, controlling the quality of returned parts, and salvaging or repairing returned products.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10219 .

ex:PCF_10349 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Plan inbound material receipts""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10349" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing the receipts of inbound materials. Create a plan accounting for the materials procured from the source of supply and the materials delivered to the distribution center or the warehouse.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20936 .

ex:PCF_10350 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage inbound material flow""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10350" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing all the internal activities related to the flow/transfer of materials. Manage materials being delivered to distribution center or warehouse. Gauge the time taken for delivery and if the delivery process is on time. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20936 .

ex:PCF_10351 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Monitor inbound delivery performance""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10351" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Overseeing the performance of an inbound delivery system. Check the present delivery system's efficiency, cost effectiveness, and adherence to a delivery schedule.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20936 .

ex:PCF_10352 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage flow of returned products""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10352" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.2.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Tracking and taking care of the products that have been internally returned either because of their deficiency or in cases of incorrect delivery. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20936 .

ex:PCF_20109 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage disposition of returned products""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20109" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.2.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining if a returned product can be salvaged or repaired. Salvage or repair is dependent upon the product, the condition of the product, or the availability of a like item.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20936 .

ex:PCF_12708 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Determine quality of controlled part""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12708" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.2.5.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Implement a checks and balances system to verify that returned parts meet acceptable quality standards to determine appropriate disposition activity.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20109 .

ex:PCF_10366 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Perform salvage activities""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10366" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.2.5.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Executing activities for reinstating the returned products. Present the customer with additional incentives of compensation in case of any defective products delivery or any discrepancy in the product specifications in order to save the order from being permanently returned.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20109 .

ex:PCF_21604 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage repair/refurbishment""" ;
    ex:pcfID "21604" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.2.5.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Administering the reinstatement of the returned product in order to return them back to customers. Repair or remanufacture the defective or ineffective products returned by the customer. Process the delivery of the repaired or remanufactured products back to the customer.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20109 .

ex:PCF_21605 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Return to finished goods inventory""" ;
    ex:pcfID "21605" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.2.5.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Moving a returned product back to inventory or stock. Whether a product is sufficient as returned, repaired, or refurbished, moving that product back to inventory for resale or returning to customer is the fnal step in Manage disposition of returned products.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20109 .

ex:PCF_10340 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Operate warehousing""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10340" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Tracking the inventory deployment. Accept and store products. Ship the products. Measure the accuracy of the inventory. Assess the performance of the outsourced logistics activities.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10219 .

ex:PCF_10353 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage and track inventory deployment""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10353" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Tracking the logistical act of delivering or releasing an inventory item or entity to targeted end users. Track how much inventory has been deployed at all the distribution centers, individually.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10340 .

ex:PCF_10354 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Receive, inspect, and store inbound deliveries""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10354" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Coordinating the incoming inbound materials/products. Accept the delivery of these materials and the subsequent storage. Track them at the warehouse/distribution center. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10340 .

ex:PCF_10355 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Track product availability""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10355" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Keeping track of the availability of different materials/products at the warehouse and distribution centers. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10340 .

ex:PCF_10356 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Pick, pack, and ship product for delivery""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10356" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.3.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Packing and shipping the product to deliver to the customer. Take care of the internal and external packaging of the products in order to ensure safe transportation of the products from the warehouse to delivery locations. Notify the ERP system and/or Accounts Receivable Dept.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10340 .

ex:PCF_10357 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Track inventory accuracy""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10357" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.3.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Monitoring any discrepancies between electronic records that represent the inventory and the physical state of the inventory. Look for discrepancies such as phantom inventory, which includes products that an inventory accounting system considers to be available at the storage location but are not actually available.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10340 .

ex:PCF_10358 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Track third-party logistics storage and shipping performance""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10358" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.3.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Keeping a track on the storage and shipping performance of third-party agencies. Monitor logistics storage and shipping performance for third-party agencies. Use measures such as a logistics scoreboard, activity-based costing, economic value analysis, and balanced scorecards.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10340 .

ex:PCF_10359 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage physical finished goods inventory""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10359" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.3.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Administering the movement of the finished products that are processed by the organization through its warehouses. Track goods through the use of systems such as barcodes in order to monitor the volumes available, quantity of out-flowing goods, remaining shelf life of the product, etc.--ultimately, to best manage the warehouse capacity.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10340 .

ex:PCF_20957 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage warehouse transfers""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20957" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.3.8" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Shipping items from one warehouse to another in a multi-warehouse environment. A warehouse transfer is typically handled electronically in a system designed to replicate the physical processes involved with transferring items from one warehouse to another.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10340 .

ex:PCF_10341 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Operate outbound transportation""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10341" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating a plan that specifies the schedule and system for transportation and delivery of the outbound products, as well as tracking the performance of the carrier delivery system. Conduct vehicle management and processing of all carrier-related documents.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10219 .

ex:PCF_10360 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Plan, transport, and deliver outbound product""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10360" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.4.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Organizing the transportation and delivery of outbound products. Plan and organize the transportation, shipping, and delivery of the end products. Create a plan that specifies dispatch and delivery of the product to its destination, as well the transportation.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10341 .

ex:PCF_10361 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Track carrier delivery performance""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10361" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.4.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Monitoring delivery performance when carrying products from the warehouse/distribution centers to the retailers or end consumers. Create a performance metrics based on the key performance indicators.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10341 .

ex:PCF_10362 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage transportation fleet""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10362" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.4.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Taking care of a range of functions related to the means of transport used for delivering the end products. Manage vehicle financing, vehicle maintenance, vehicle telematics (tracking and diagnostics), driver management, speed management, fuel management, and health and safety management.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10341 .

ex:PCF_10363 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Process and audit carrier invoices and documents""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10363" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "4.4.4.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Organizing and inspecting all account statements and any other documentation for the carriers used in delivery. Create, manage, and inspect all documents related to the financial, regulatory, and administrative accounts of all the carriers/freights. Generate receipts for all freight transactions.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10341 .

ex:PCF_20025 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Deliver Services""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20025" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.0" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Category" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Offering services to customers. This is the act of providing service delivery as a core business practice and covers identifying strategies for performing service delivery, managing resources, and delivering services to the customer.""" .

ex:PCF_20026 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish service delivery governance and strategies""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20026" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating rules and regulations for service delivery to the customer. Establish a system to manage performance, delivery, and direction of service delivery. Engage with the customer for satisfaction feedback. Define goals, policies, processes, and workplace layout and infrastructure as a part of the service delivery strategy.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20025 .

ex:PCF_20027 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish service delivery governance""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20027" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Establishing service delivery governance through a system that manages performance, development, and direction. Allow for customer feedback on delivery satisfaction.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20026 .

ex:PCF_20028 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Set up and maintain service delivery governance and management system""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20028" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.1.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Providing a system for which to manage customer needs and a structure for which to facilitate service delivery to fulfill those needs.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20027 .

ex:PCF_20029 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage service delivery performance""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20029" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.1.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Conducting and implementing performance measures to ensure successful delivery of service to the customer.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20027 .

ex:PCF_20030 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage service delivery development and direction""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20030" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.1.1.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Providing guidance of resources to ensure that the development and direction of service delivery is in line with customer needs.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20027 .

ex:PCF_20031 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Solicit feedback from customer on service delivery satisfaction""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20031" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.1.1.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Engaging the customer post delivery to gauge the effectiveness of services rendered in order to improve on key delivery functions going forward.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20027 .

ex:PCF_20032 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop service delivery strategies""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20032" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Constructing strategies that identify goals, policies, processes, and procedures in relation to service delivery. Review and validate strategies. Define the workplace layout and infrastructure.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20026 .

ex:PCF_20033 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define service delivery goals""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20033" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.1.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Aligning organization practices to meet the needs of the customer by creating service delivery goals.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20032 .

ex:PCF_20034 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define labor policies""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20034" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.1.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Outlining labor policies for resources and ensuring that those policies meet the needs of the organization, the customer, and government regulations.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20032 .

ex:PCF_20035 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Evaluate resource availability""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20035" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.1.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Understanding the needs of the customer and providing the necessary resources to meet those requirements. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20032 .

ex:PCF_20036 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define service delivery network and supply constraints""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20036" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.1.2.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Identifying and understanding the limitations imposed upon service delivery network and supply.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20032 .

ex:PCF_20037 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define service delivery process""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20037" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.1.2.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Defanging policies and procedures that focus on meeting the needs and expectations of the customer within the working parameters of the organization.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20032 .

ex:PCF_20038 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Review and validate service delivery procedures""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20038" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.1.2.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Revisioning service delivery procedures that fall short of performance parameters. Realign procedures with specified expectations in order to provide successful service delivery. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20032 .

ex:PCF_20039 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define service delivery workplace layout and infrastructure""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20039" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.1.2.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating a workplace that best serves the needs of the organization and customer through strategic layout and infrastructure. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20032 .

ex:PCF_20040 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage service delivery resources""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20040" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Understanding the demands on resources and creating a plan to enable the delivery of services via those resources.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20025 .

ex:PCF_20041 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage service delivery resource demand""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20041" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Ensuring necessary resources are maintained through monitoring pipeline, developing forecasts, and collaborating with customers. Determine skills needed for service deliver and forecast customer orders. Monitor forecasted orders and modify if where needed. Measure forecast accuracy. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20040 .

ex:PCF_20042 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Monitor pipeline""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20042" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Tracking potential opportunities as they move through the various stages of the pipeline. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20041 .

ex:PCF_20043 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop baseline forecasts""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20043" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Identifying the demand anticipated for the organization's services. Estimate future demand for services using historical data, analysis of the market environment, and external data.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20041 .

ex:PCF_20044 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Collaborate with customers""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20044" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.1.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Providing a collaborative meeting in which to engage the customer to understand the scope of their needs and constructing solutions based on need and constraints.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20041 .

ex:PCF_20045 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop consensus forecast""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20045" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.1.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Arriving at a consensus over the forecasted levels of demand for services by analyzing baseline forecasts and customer input. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20041 .

ex:PCF_20046 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Determine availability of skills to deliver on current and forecast customer orders""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20046" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.1.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Identifying what skillset is necessary for the delivery of opportunities. Determine the forecast of customer orders based upon those skillsets and the resources available.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20041 .

ex:PCF_20047 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Monitor activity against forecast and revise forecast""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20047" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.1.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Overseeing all activities necessary to deliver services to customer. Revise forecast to account for any issues that may arise. This could be changes in market trend, resource changes, etc. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20041 .

ex:PCF_20048 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Evaluate and revise forecasting approach""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20048" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.1.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Recognizing potential problems in the current forecast and making the necessary changes to align the forecast meet demand.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20041 .

ex:PCF_20049 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Measure forecast accuracy""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20049" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.1.8" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Analyzing forecasting against actuals to determine accuracy. Modify forecasting to align with actual need. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20041 .

ex:PCF_20050 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Create and manage resource plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20050" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Identifying the need for and creating a resource plan. Understand resource demand and align with capacity, skills, and capabilities. Enlist suppliers and partners to supplement needed skills and capabilities. Monitor and manage capabilities and skills with an eye on critical resources and supplier capacity.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20040 .

ex:PCF_20051 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define and manage skills taxonomy""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20051" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Analyzing the skills needed to perform services to be delivered. Classify and organize these skills requirements.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20050 .

ex:PCF_20052 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Create resource plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20052" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating a plan to ensure that all resources are available to carry out services required for the customer. This can include physical resources and personnel.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20050 .

ex:PCF_20053 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Match resource demand with capacity, skills, and capabilities""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20053" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Matching demand with skills and capability. Enlisting suppliers and partners to help with demand when needed.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20050 .

ex:PCF_20054 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Collaborate with suppliers and partners to supplement skills and capabilities""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20054" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.2.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Understanding organizational need to enlist suppliers to provide resources for gaps in skills and capabilities. Identify where additional skills are needed and collaborate with third parties to fill those demands.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20050 .

ex:PCF_20055 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Identify critical resources and supplier capacity""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20055" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.2.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Realizing critical resources required to perform and carry out customer needs. Engage with suppliers to fulfill those needs, if necessary. Identify supplier threshold for performing those needs.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20050 .

ex:PCF_20056 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Monitor and manage resource capacity and availability""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20056" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.2.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Directing and managing workforce needs. Ensure that resources are at full capacity. Monitor that all resources are able to skilled in their respective rolls. Make sure that necessary resources are available to provide the needed services.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20050 .

ex:PCF_12127 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Enable service delivery resources""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12127" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Instituting training to enable resources to provide service delivery to the customer. Develop a training plan. Create materials that provide for operation and technical training. Schedule, perform, and evaluate training.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20040 .

ex:PCF_12128 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop service delivery training plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12128" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating a detailed summary of all the actions relevant to teaching a person a particular skill or type of behavior. Determine who will deliver the training. Determine when and where the apprentice or trainee needs to go to receive the structured component of the training.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12127 .

ex:PCF_12129 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop training materials""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12129" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Developing materials necessary to provide comprehensive training for the skills or behavior needed to deliver services. This can be any number for formats such as classroom or computer based training.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12127 .

ex:PCF_12131 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage training schedule""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12131" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Providing training to the employee within a manageable timeframe to meet the needs of both the individual and the organization. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12127 .

ex:PCF_12132 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Deliver operations training""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12132" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.3.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Educating service delivery personnel on all aspects of the operations process of the organization.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12127 .

ex:PCF_12133 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Deliver technical training""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12133" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.3.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Ensuring that all personnel are trained on all technical aspects of service delivery.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12127 .

ex:PCF_20057 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Perform skill and capability testing""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20057" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.3.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Verifying that training provided to the person was successful through the administration testing and the application of skills for practical use.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12127 .

ex:PCF_12135 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Evaluate training effectiveness""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12135" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.2.3.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Eliciting feedback from various sources to evaluate the training provided. This can be achieved through testing and the practical application of skills. Additionally, manager or student feedback can be garnered to evaluate training effectiveness.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12127 .

ex:PCF_20058 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Deliver service to customer""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20058" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Rendering service to the customer by initiating, executing, and completing tasks associated with service delivery.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20025 .

ex:PCF_20059 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Initiate service delivery""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20059" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Collaborating with the customer to understand service needs. Review, understand, and modify the delivery scope with the organization needs of the customer in mind. Confirm readiness and identify, select, and assign resources. Plan for service delivery.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20058 .

ex:PCF_20060 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Review contract and agreed terms""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20060" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Meeting with the customer, partner, and/or supplier to review the terms of the solutions contract and agree on the terms set forth.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20059 .

ex:PCF_20061 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Understand customer requirements and define refine approach""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20061" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Taking the customer requirements for a solution and applying those requirements to a refined approach for service. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20059 .

ex:PCF_20062 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Modify/revise and approve project plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20062" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.1.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Updating the project plan to align with the new solution approach agreed upon with the customer.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20059 .

ex:PCF_20063 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Review customer business objectives""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20063" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.1.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Aligning the customer business objectives with the agreed service delivery solution.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20059 .

ex:PCF_20064 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Confirm environmental readiness""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20064" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.1.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Confirming that the organization has the recourses necessary to meet the expectations for the solution for service delivery.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20059 .

ex:PCF_20065 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Identify, select, and assign resources""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20065" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.1.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Identifying, selecting, and assigning resources required to deliver service to the customer. Ensure that all objectives are established and met, and the all rules of engagement have been identified and communicated.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20059 .

ex:PCF_20066 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish people objectives""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20066" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.1.6.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Providing the workforce with a plan of action and goals necessary to provide a service. Make sure that those objectives are met.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20065 .

ex:PCF_20067 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish engagement rules""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20067" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.1.6.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Establishing guidelines for how resources engage with the customer. For example, set rules of accountability, interaction, and accommodation when engaging the customer. Resources should be polite, empathetic, and attentive.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20065 .

ex:PCF_20068 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Plan for service delivery""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20068" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.1.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Establishing a plan of action to successfully render a solution for service delivery.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20059 .

ex:PCF_20069 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Execute service delivery""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20069" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Carrying out service delivery to the customer by creating and deploying the necessary solution. Analyze need and create a solution. Validate the solution and make changes if needed. Obtain approval to build/buy solution and then deploy solution to customer.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20058 .

ex:PCF_20070 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Analyze environment and customer needs""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20070" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Understanding the needs of the customer and providing the necessary resources to meet those requirements within the scope of the organization. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20069 .

ex:PCF_20071 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define solution""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20071" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating a plan of action to provide service delivery to the customer through a possible solution. This solution should be in response to a collaborative effort made by the organization and the customer to meet service delivery needs.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20069 .

ex:PCF_20072 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Validate solution""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20072" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Validating that the proposed solution is feasible and provides the needed services for the customer.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20069 .

ex:PCF_20073 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Identify changes""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20073" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.2.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Realizing issues within the original drafted solution and providing changes to correct those issues.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20069 .

ex:PCF_20074 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Obtain approval to proceed""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20074" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.2.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Gaining approval from all avenues to proceed with providing solutions for service delivery.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20069 .

ex:PCF_20075 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Make build/buy solution""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20075" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.2.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Constructing or purchasing solutions necessary to provide service delivery.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20069 .

ex:PCF_20076 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Deploy solution""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20076" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.2.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Providing the customer with promised services and solutions. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20069 .

ex:PCF_20077 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Complete service delivery""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20077" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Implementing final steps to complete service delivery to the customer. Evaluate success through project review, complete finance activities, and confirm delivery. Release resources and manage completion by harvesting knowledge and systems by archiving records.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20058 .

ex:PCF_20078 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Conduct service delivery/project review and evaluate success""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20078" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Reviewing the entire service delivery process to evaluate the success of the project from beginning to end.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20077 .

ex:PCF_20079 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Complete/finalize financial management activities""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20079" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Insuring all payments are received and all activates therein are completed. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20077 .

ex:PCF_20080 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Confirm delivery according to contract terms""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20080" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Confirming that the organization has satisfied all terms of the delivery contract set forth in collaboration between the organization and customer.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20077 .

ex:PCF_20081 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Release resources""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20081" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.3.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Discharging leveraged resources from service delivery commitments upon completion. Returning resources to the resource pool.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20077 .

ex:PCF_20082 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage service delivery completion""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20082" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.3.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Ensuring that all aspects of the service delivery process are completed both internally and externally.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20077 .

ex:PCF_20083 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Harvest knowledge""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20083" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.3.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Garnering feedback from all avenues to collect a knowledge base concerning services rendered.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20077 .

ex:PCF_20084 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Archive records and update systems""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20084" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "5.3.3.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Completing and archiving all records associated with requested services. Update all necessary systems to reflect those changes.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20077 .

ex:PCF_20085 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage Customer Service""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20085" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.0" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Category" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing customers before and after the delivery of services. This includes developing and planning customer service practices with an eye on steering processes relating to inquiries after sales, feedback, warranties, and recalls. """ .

ex:PCF_10378 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop customer service strategy""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10378" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Defining a plan that removes customer obstacles by gathering operational insight and competitive insight, as well as improving soft skills and forward resolution for employees. Develop customer segmentation. Define rules and regulations for customer service. Establish service levels for customers.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20085 .

ex:PCF_20086 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define customer service requirements across the enterprise""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20086" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Defining a set of behaviors, skills, and policies needed to provide customer service effectively across the enterprise.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10378 .

ex:PCF_20087 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define customer service experience""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20087" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Communicating to the customer service resources what is expected when engaging the customer. Relate service level expectations to the workforce. Ensure positive customer experience. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10378 .

ex:PCF_20088 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define and manage customer service channel strategy""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20088" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.1.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Establishing and refining procedures for customer service and technical support.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10378 .

ex:PCF_10382 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define customer service policies and procedures""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10382" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.1.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Outlining the framework of policies and methods for developing customer service strategy. Establish the rules and regulations that serve as a guideline for the customer service strategy. Take into account customer needs and behavior.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10378 .

ex:PCF_10383 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish target service level for each customer segment""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10383" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.1.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining and implementing levels for customer services. Benchmark certain customer service practices, and base customer level services on those benchmarks. Create a service level agreement, which is a negotiated agreement designed to create a common understanding about services, priorities, and responsibilities.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10378 .

ex:PCF_20089 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define warranty claims""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20089" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.1.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining the exact terms and conditions under which specific warranties apply to certain goods or services.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10378 .

ex:PCF_16893 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Determine and document warranty policies""" ;
    ex:pcfID "16893" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.1.6.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Establishing warranty policies to assure customers that the company will guarantee its warranties that it issues. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20089 .

ex:PCF_16890 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Create and manage warranty rules/claim codes for products""" ;
    ex:pcfID "16890" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.1.6.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Establishing and maintaining claims processing and routing rules. Establish and maintain claims processing and routing rules for product warranties, coverage lists, repair, fault, trouble codes, repair time setup, and warranty policy registration. This also includes rolling out the codes and rules, and the improvements/updates to these rules and codes via systematic updates.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20089 .

ex:PCF_20090 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Agree on warranty responsibilities with suppliers""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20090" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.1.6.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Negotiating with manufacturers and dealers the obligations of each party in upholding warranties.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20089 .

ex:PCF_20091 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define warranty related offerings for customers""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20091" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.1.6.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Informing customers about warranties that apply to promoted products or services.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20089 .

ex:PCF_12673 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Communicate warranty policies and offerings""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12673" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.1.6.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Communicating rules and updates via training manuals for new products and training resources.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20089 .

ex:PCF_20092 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop recall strategy""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20092" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.1.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Establishing procedures to handle recalls of defective products.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10378 .

ex:PCF_10379 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Plan and manage customer service contacts""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10379" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Planning and administering work force operations for customer service provision by taking care of customer services requests/inquiries, as well as the complaints.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20085 .

ex:PCF_10387 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Plan and manage customer service work force""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10387" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and administering the work force deployed for the customer service process. Forecast the customer work force needs to correctly schedule the work force. Track the utility of the work force deployed. Examine the interactions between the customer and customer service representatives to achieve high quality.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10379 .

ex:PCF_10390 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Forecast volume of customer service contacts""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10390" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Projecting the total work force required to service customer service inquiries in order to effectively predict the volume of vendor contracts required. Estimate the number of the customer service contracts in an agreed-upon time frame in order to strategically maintain the work force necessitated for customer inquires. Analyze historical data around customer service contracts, the universe of customer inquiries, frequency of inquiries, servicing capability (per head) of the employees, etc.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10387 .

ex:PCF_10391 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Schedule customer service work force""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10391" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Deploying the work force to manage customer service contracts. Create a systematic summary of the operations and service required, as well as the specific amount of work force that is to be deployed to the customer service operations. Ensure work force is directly proportional to the estimated forecast of customer service contracts.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10387 .

ex:PCF_10392 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Track work force utilization""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10392" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.1.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Tracking the utilization of work force deployed for managing customer service operations. Monitor the utility of the work force deployed for managing customer service operations in order to evaluate its efficiency and cost effectiveness. Calculate the overall labor effectiveness, which measures the utility, performance, and quality of the work force.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10387 .

ex:PCF_10393 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Monitor and evaluate quality of customer interactions with customer service representatives""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10393" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.1.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Tracking and determining the quality of interactions between the customer and customer representatives. Use electronic devices to record and effectively assess customer representatives' interactions. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10387 .

ex:PCF_10388 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage customer service problems, requests, and inquiries""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10388" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Handling the requests and inquiries from customers that seek information regarding the organization's products/services. Obtain the customer requests online and by phone. Direct these requests to higher-level representatives. Approve requests, and respond to customers.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10379 .

ex:PCF_10394 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Receive customer problems, requests, and inquiries""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10394" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Receiving requests for information from customers over multiple channels. Receive various requests and inquiries from customers regarding products/services. Accept these inquiries through channels such as email, telephone, online forms, text messages, social media, and in person. Supply dedicated equipment, systems, and personnel.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10388 .

ex:PCF_13482 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Analyze problems, requests, and inquiries""" ;
    ex:pcfID "13482" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Analyzing various requests and inquiries from customers regarding products/services. Provide answers and offerings to satisfy the customer's needs. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10388 .

ex:PCF_10395 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Resolve customer problems, requests, and inquiries""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10395" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Routing customer inquiries in order to service them with the most apposite response. Direct customer inquires to the best suited personnel or system. Have a system or procedure capable of efficiently channeling these requests.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10388 .

ex:PCF_10396 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Respond to customer problems, requests, and inquiries""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10396" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.2.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Responding to customer requests by email, conversation, interactive voice response, mail, etc. with the most appropriate reply. Instill a robust process to locate the right information for a solution to a customer's problem.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10388 .

ex:PCF_16928 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Identify and capture upsell/cross-sell opportunities""" ;
    ex:pcfID "16928" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.2.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Utilizing customer inquiries as opportunities to either provide a comparable service to the one in question, offer additional complimentary service, or suggest a service that is better than what was initially offered.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10388 .

ex:PCF_16937 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Deliver opportunity to sales team""" ;
    ex:pcfID "16937" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.2.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Providing possible sales leads to the sales team in an effort to garner more business opportunities.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10388 .

ex:PCF_10389 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage customer complaints""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10389" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Obtaining customer complaints online or by phone. Direct these complaints to higher-level representatives as appropriate. Resolve them. Respond to customers.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10379 .

ex:PCF_10397 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Receive customer complaints""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10397" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Receiving any complaints or grievances from customers for the organization's products/services. Receive objections, complaints, and criticism from customers regarding products/services through email, telephone, online forms, text messages, social media, in person, etc. Dedicate equipment, systems, and personnel.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10389 .

ex:PCF_10398 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Route customer complaints""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10398" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Routing any complaints or grievances received from customers in order to address them in the most appropriate manner. Direct complaints to the best suited personnel or system. Implement a system or procedure capable of efficiently channeling the various objections, complaints, and criticism from customers over the offerings provided by the organization.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10389 .

ex:PCF_10399 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Resolve customer complaints""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10399" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Resolving any customer complaints that are deemed to be sound and reasonable. Redress any objections, grievances, and complaints received from customers regarding the offerings provided by the organization. Identify the legitimate complaints, where the situation needs to be appropriately corrected. Deploy personnel who can rectify the issue within a stipulated time frame.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10389 .

ex:PCF_10400 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Respond to customer complaints""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10400" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.3.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Responding to customer complaints including all activities necessitated to service any objections, complaints, or grievances with the most appropriate reply. Source the right information to formulate a response that eases the discomfort being experienced by the customer. (Closely coordinate with Resolve customer complaints [10399].)""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10389 .

ex:PCF_19072 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Analyze customer complaints and response/redressal""" ;
    ex:pcfID "19072" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.3.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Analyzing complaint logs to provide input for continuous service improvement and customer profiling.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10389 .

ex:PCF_20094 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Process returns""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20094" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Acquiring returns and identify if the returns are scraped or salvaged.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10379 .

ex:PCF_10364 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Authorize return""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10364" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.4.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Approving and carrying forward the requests by the customers to return the product. This is part of the process of returning a product in order to receive a refund, replacement, or repair during the product's warranty period.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20094 .

ex:PCF_20095 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Process return and record reason""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20095" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.4.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Notating the reason for the return of the product.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20094 .

ex:PCF_12840 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Report incidents and risks to regulatory bodies""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12840" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.2.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Notifying all stakeholders, legal, and industry regulatory bodies of the incidents and risks related to a return or recall, if needed. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10379 .

ex:PCF_12658 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Service products after sales""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12658" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Assigning post-sales policies and paying claims on purchased products.  This is a process that is an administrative function focused on creating rules (claim codes). This group ensures that claims are valid and are processed quickly.  As well as to quickly determine responsibility for claim settlement. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20085 .

ex:PCF_20605 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Register products""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20605" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Filing product registrations.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12658 .

ex:PCF_12669 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Process warranty claims""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12669" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Identifying, investigating, and processes warranty claims. This process includes: receipt and validation of a warranty claim; definition and diagnosis /root cause analysis of an issue and recommendation for corrective action; the determination of responsibility for settlement of the claim; the transaction being approved or denied; and the originator being notified and payment authorized. In the case of a recurring event, further investigation (definition and diagnosis or root cause analysis) is performed, and a recommendation for corrective action is made and implemented in production/design. It ends when the claim is closed.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12658 .

ex:PCF_20096 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Receive warranty claim""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20096" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Receiving incoming warranty claims. Route claim to correct department. Document claim.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12669 .

ex:PCF_12671 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Validate warranty claim""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12671" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Ensuring that the claim falls within the parameters of the warranty in question. After validation is made, the claim must be investigated.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12669 .

ex:PCF_20097 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Investigate warranty issues""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20097" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Executing investigational and analysis of warranty claims. This involves notification and definition of a warranty issue, includes the scheduling of a field service agent to perform further investigation; the request and receipt of defective parts; and diagnosis/root cause analysis. This concludes with the receipt of the result and recommendation for corrective action.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12669 .

ex:PCF_20098 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define issue""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20098" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.2.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Defining the issue of the claim. The warranty team will look into the issue and understand whether it is covered by the claim code or if more detail is required. Field service will be scheduled to further qualify the definition of the issue and to collect more evidence.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20097 .

ex:PCF_12677 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Schedule field service""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12677" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.2.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Scheduling additional investigative field service. This is performed for high priority claims or claims that require additional investigation. Field service engineers will gather additional information, perform further investigation, and qualify the definition of the issue.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20097 .

ex:PCF_12678 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Request and receive defective part""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12678" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.2.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Requesting receipt of a defective part for further investigation.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20097 .

ex:PCF_20099 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Investigate issue/perform root cause analysis""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20099" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.2.3.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Investigating claims by an appropriate functional representative. Once the issue has been clearly defined and diagnosed and a recommendation for corrective action is determined, it will be provided to the warranty management team.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20097 .

ex:PCF_20100 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Receive investigation result/recommendation for corrective action""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20100" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.2.3.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Receiving investigative results to assess claim approval or denial. The warranty team will assess the results of the investigation and the recommendations for corrective action.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20097 .

ex:PCF_20101 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Determine responsible party""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20101" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.2.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Identifying responsible party for a claim. There is no negotiation with the supplier at this point. There can be multiple warranties applicable to the same part: a new part warranty, a new product warranty (for the product the part is installed on), and a supplier warranty from the company that last repaired the part. The information required for this decision would be the output of Receive component/part and analyze fault [19728].\"""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12669 .

ex:PCF_20102 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage pre-authorizations""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20102" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.2.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Authorizing claims prior to submittal. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12669 .

ex:PCF_12668 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Approve or reject warranty claim""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12668" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.2.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Following Defining issue [20098], an approval or rejection with be made against the warranty claim. If it is deemed that the claim falls within the warranty parameters, the claim will be approved. If the claim is deemed to fall outside warranty parameters, the claim with be rejected.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12669 .

ex:PCF_20103 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Notify originator of approve/reject decision""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20103" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.2.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Contacting the originator of whether the warranty claim has been approved or rejected.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12669 .

ex:PCF_20104 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Authorize payment""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20104" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.2.8" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Allowing for a payment to be made to the claimant.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12669 .

ex:PCF_20105 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Close claim""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20105" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.2.9" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Archiving and closing the warranty claim after a final decision has been made to either approve or reject. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12669 .

ex:PCF_12667 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Reconcile warranty transaction disposition""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12667" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.2.10" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Assuring that the warranty transaction has been completed.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12669 .

ex:PCF_20106 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage supplier recovery""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20106" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing the recovery of costs from suppliers for individual claims.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12658 .

ex:PCF_20107 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Create supplier recovery claims""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20107" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Raising a supplier recovery claim. This is based off the decision made in Receive investigation result/recommendation for corrective action [20100].""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20106 .

ex:PCF_20108 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Negotiate recoveries with suppliers""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20108" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Arranging the returns of recalled products to suppliers.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20106 .

ex:PCF_10218 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Service products""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10218" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Validating specific service requirements for individual customers. Determine and schedule resource to fulfill these requirements. Provide service to specific individual customers. Ensure the quality of service delivery.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12658 .

ex:PCF_10320 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Confirm specific service requirements for individual customer""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10320" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Acquiring or soliciting information about specific service requirements for individual customers through the customer service function. Obtain information about customer specific requests, process these requests, and create customer profiles to generate a service order.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10218 .

ex:PCF_10324 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Process customer request""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10324" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Soliciting or acquiring information using various sources such as databases, customer interactions, and customer request forms. Hand them further up the hierarchy to deal with them. Categorize the user's request, determining if the request is supportable and prioritizing the request.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10320 .

ex:PCF_10325 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Create customer profile""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10325" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Documenting the individual customer service requirements solicited, along with personal information of the customers, in order to generate customized profiles that hasten the delivery process.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10320 .

ex:PCF_10326 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Generate service order""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10326" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4.1.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Designing a short-term agreement between the service provider and customer. One-time services are ordered by the service recipient and resource-related billing is performed upon completion. Use the service order to document service and customer service work.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10320 .

ex:PCF_10321 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Identify and schedule resources to meet service requirements""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10321" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining and scheduling the resources required to fulfill customer service requirements. Create a detailed schedule about the service orders and development of these service orders. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10218 .

ex:PCF_10327 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Create resourcing plan and schedule""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10327" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Developing a plan for sourcing and deploying the resources required to fulfill customer service needs. Document a detailed summary of all types of resources (equipment, finance, personnel, time, etc.) required to complete customer service requests and procure these resources. Identify and assess various sources in order to effectively create a resourcing plan.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10321 .

ex:PCF_10328 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Create service order fulfillment schedule""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10328" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Designing a detailed summary of customer service order requirements, along with information concerning the timing and duration for these services. Categorize the customer needs. Monitor the services delivered.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10321 .

ex:PCF_10322 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Provide service to specific customers""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10322" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Dispatching resources for managing and fulfilling daily service requirements. Manage the progress of order fulfillment. Complete order blocks. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10218 .

ex:PCF_10330 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Organize daily service order fulfillment schedule""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10330" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Laying out a daily plan of specific service orders that need to be fulfilled. Document and systematically order these activities to ensure high effectiveness and efficiency.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10322 .

ex:PCF_10331 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Execute product repair""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10331" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Dispatching and delivering the resources needed for the specific service requirements from the source/warehouse. Manage the dispatch, transportation, and delivery of the services.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10322 .

ex:PCF_10332 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage service order fulfillment""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10332" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Handling and managing orders fulfilled, along with the orders are not or partially fulfilled to track the order fulfillment progress. Use electronic devices such as trackers and GPS in order track and ensure delivery of the orders.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10322 .

ex:PCF_10323 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Ensure quality of service""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10323" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Guaranteeing the quality of service provided to customers. Identify the successful and unsuccessful orders along with the service failures. Collect customer feedback. Process the feedback to ensure the quality of service in the future. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10218 .

ex:PCF_10334 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Identify completed service orders for feedback""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10334" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4.4.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining the service orders that have been successfully delivered. Identify the service orders completed and delivered to the customer. Leverage communication systems to ensure coordination with the customers in order to avoid mishaps.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10323 .

ex:PCF_10335 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Identify incomplete service orders and service failures""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10335" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4.4.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining orders which have not been completed or delivered. Identify the service orders that are partially or entirely incomplete, as well as the orders that have not been delivered to the customer. Use techniques such as project trackers to recognize the progress of the service orders.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10323 .

ex:PCF_10336 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Solicit customer feedback on services delivered""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10336" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4.4.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Obtaining and procuring customer reviews or feedback on the services delivered. Design a customer feedback form, or communicate with the customer through the phone or online.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10323 .

ex:PCF_10337 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Process customer feedback on services delivered""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10337" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.3.4.4.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Assessing and incorporating customer reviews/feedback into the service plan to ensure high quality of service. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10323 .

ex:PCF_20110 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage product recalls and regulatory audits""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20110" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Removing defective products from the distribution chain. Participate in audits from watchdog agencies.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20085 .

ex:PCF_20111 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Initiate recall""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20111" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.4.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Commencing the removal process of defective products.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20110 .

ex:PCF_20112 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Assess the likelihood and consequences of occurrence of any hazards""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20112" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.4.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Performing risk analysis. Identify all dangers, evaluate how probable they are, and what kinds of negative results or or adverse side effect they carry.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20110 .

ex:PCF_20113 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage recall related communications""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20113" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.4.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Handling communications that are related to product recalls.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20110 .

ex:PCF_20114 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Submit regulatory reports""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20114" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.4.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and delivering reports to regulatory agencies to provide details about handling product recalls. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20110 .

ex:PCF_20115 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Monitor and audit recall effectiveness""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20115" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.4.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Analyzing the effectiveness of product recalls.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20110 .

ex:PCF_20116 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage recall termination""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20116" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.4.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Ending product recalls, communicating to the public and filing reports.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20110 .

ex:PCF_20595 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Evaluate customer service operations and customer satisfaction""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20595" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Calculating and assessing the operational activities of the customer service function. Evaluation is achieved through the customer requests/inquiries handling process, the customer complaint handling process, and product and services quality. Examine activities to ensure high levels of customer service.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20085 .

ex:PCF_10401 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Measure customer satisfaction with customer problems, requests, and inquiries handling""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10401" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Calculating satisfaction levels of customers by effectively evaluating the process of handling requests/inquiries of customers. Effectively calculate the performance of customer-requests/inquiries handling and resolution. Obtain information regarding requests/inquiries handling and resolution through customer feedback. Use it to explore new ideas and opportunities for enhanced customer requests/inquiries handling and resolution process.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20595 .

ex:PCF_11687 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Solicit customer feedback on customer service experience""" ;
    ex:pcfID "11687" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating an avenue for which the customer can provide feedback on their experience with how their inquiry, problem, or request was handled. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10401 .

ex:PCF_11688 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Analyze customer service data and identify improvement opportunities""" ;
    ex:pcfID "11688" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Reviewing customer service feedback to identify areas in which improvements can be made. Engage with management to discuss issues.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10401 .

ex:PCF_18126 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Provide customer feedback to product management on customer service experience""" ;
    ex:pcfID "18126" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.1.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Handing over data to management to analyze common issues in regards to customer service.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10401 .

ex:PCF_10402 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Measure customer satisfaction with customer- complaint handling and resolution""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10402" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Measuring the satisfaction level of customers as pertains to how their complaints are handled and resolved. This process element requires the organization to estimate the customers level of fulfillment with the process reconciling their complaints and towards the objective of ensuring customer retention. The feedback received can be used to develop concepts for new opportunities to boost the level of customer satisfaction.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20595 .

ex:PCF_11236 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Solicit customer feedback on complaint handling and resolution""" ;
    ex:pcfID "11236" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Requesting customer feedback on the process of handling and resolving customer complaints. Obtain information about the effectiveness and performance of the customer complaint handling process from the customers through various means (e.g., online and by phone).""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10402 .

ex:PCF_11237 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Analyze customer complaint data and identify improvement opportunities""" ;
    ex:pcfID "11237" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Examining the information obtained through handling and resolving complaints for development/improvement opportunities. Categorize the customer complaints data on the basis of speed, accuracy, courtesy, price, product choice, availability, hours, location, etc. Determine complaint patterns in order to diagnose areas needing enhancement.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10402 .

ex:PCF_11689 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Identify common customer complaints""" ;
    ex:pcfID "11689" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining complaint patterns in order to identify common issues. Document common problems for correction.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10402 .

ex:PCF_10403 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Measure customer satisfaction with products and services""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10403" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Calculating satisfaction levels of customers with products/services. Obtain customer feedback on products/services, as well as the effectiveness of the advertising campaigns. Examine this information to reach meaningful conclusions, which could then be used to enhance the customer service operations.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20595 .

ex:PCF_11238 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Gather and solicit post-sale customer feedback on products and services""" ;
    ex:pcfID "11238" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Obtaining customer feedback/review on the quality and utility derived from the products/services after the sale is complete. Use techniques such as surveys, feedback boxes, and user activity and usability tests.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10403 .

ex:PCF_11239 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Solicit post-sale customer feedback on ad effectiveness""" ;
    ex:pcfID "11239" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Assessing the influence of advertisements on purchasing behavior. Use techniques such as surveys and product recognition tests, questionnaires or feedback flyers, and toll-free numbers in order to encourage customer interaction after the sale.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10403 .

ex:PCF_20117 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Solicit customer feedback on cross-channel experience""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20117" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Engaging with the customer to understand their cross-channel experience. Find out what channels were effective and what areas need improvement.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10403 .

ex:PCF_11240 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Analyze product and service satisfaction data and identify improvement opportunities""" ;
    ex:pcfID "11240" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.3.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Assessing the information collected on customer satisfaction levels with products/services in order to determine areas for improvement. Examine the data and information extracted from the customer feedback and reviews to measure the satisfaction levels of the customers. Identify opportunities that could enhance the customer satisfaction levels and the overall customer service strategy.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10403 .

ex:PCF_11241 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Provide feedback and insights to appropriate teams (product design/development, marketing, manufacturing)""" ;
    ex:pcfID "11241" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.3.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Providing feedback from customers on products/services to the product management team. Analyze information collected through Gather and solicit post-sale customer feedback on products/services [11238]. Share with the product management team for consideration while improving existing offerings or developing new products/services. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10403 .

ex:PCF_12672 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Evaluate and manage warranty performance""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12672" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Assessing the cost and effectiveness of warranties. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20595 .

ex:PCF_20118 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Measure customer satisfaction with warranty handling and resolution""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20118" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.4.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Evaluating how satisfied customers are with how product warranties are managed and resolved.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12672 .

ex:PCF_12676 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Monitor and report on warranty management metrics""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12676" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.4.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Comparing warranties by using applicable metrics to see how they are handled and resolved. Develop and submit reports that summarize significant conclusions.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12672 .

ex:PCF_20119 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Identify improvement opportunities""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20119" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.4.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining how warranties and warranty management can be made better and more efficient.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12672 .

ex:PCF_12674 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Identify opportunities to eliminate warranty waste""" ;
    ex:pcfID "12674" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.4.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Finding ways to phase out unused or seldom used warranties.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12672 .

ex:PCF_20120 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Investigate fraudulent claims""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20120" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.4.5" ;
