    ex:apqcSourceText """Reviewing and assessing claims that contain deliberately incorrect information or that have been submitted with the goal to deceive the system.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_12672 .

ex:PCF_20121 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Evaluate recall performance""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20121" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "6.5.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Reviewing customer service feedback to identify areas in which improvements can be made. Engage with management to discuss issues.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20595 .

ex:PCF_10007 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop and Manage Human Capital""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10007" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.0" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Category" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Delivering processes traditionally defined as \"human resources\". Process groups include those related to developing and maintaining workforce strategy, recruiting employees, developing and counseling employees, managing employee relations, rewarding and retaining employees, redeploying and retiring employees, managing employee information, and managing employee communications.""" .

ex:PCF_17043 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop and manage human resources planning, policies, and strategies""" ;
    ex:pcfID "17043" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating strategies for the HR function. Create and implement strategies for managing the work force. Supervise and enhance the strategies, plans, and policies supporting the HR function. Developing models for managing competency levels of the HR of the organization.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10007 .

ex:PCF_20958 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop human resources strategy""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20958" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating a long-term plan to associate human resource requirements with the strategic goals of the company to ensure that there is enough qualified staffing to achieve those goals, to maintain competitive advantage and to reduce employee turnover.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17043 .

ex:PCF_10418 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Identify strategic HR needs""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10418" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Strategically defining the current and future needs for developing an efficient HR strategy. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20958 .

ex:PCF_10419 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define HR and business function roles and accountability""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10419" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Outlining the charge and duty of the HR function by defining its responsibility areas, as well as ensuring its accountability. Establish the HR function by laying out the roles and responsibilities for this function and the rules and regulations guiding HR. Define the goals and objectives of the HR, as well as a mission and vision for this function. Create a mechanism involving a set of policies, code of conduct, and institutional procedure to ensure HR accountability.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20958 .

ex:PCF_21430 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Determine HR function roles and structure""" ;
    ex:pcfID "21430" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.1.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Establishing the roles that are required to execute the HR function.  This process also examines the organizational structure required to support the organization.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20958 .

ex:PCF_21431 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Determine HR delivery model""" ;
    ex:pcfID "21431" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.1.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining how an organization's human resources department offers services to and interacts with employees. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20958 .

ex:PCF_10420 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Determine HR costs""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10420" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.1.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Ascertaining the costs and expenses of the HR function. Identify and report HR investments using, for example, a cost approach or a present value of future earnings approach.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20958 .

ex:PCF_10421 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish HR measures""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10421" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.1.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Evaluating the performance of HR function. Lay out the course of HR procedures that would formulate a plan of action needed to fulfill strategic HR needs. Deploy measures such as hiring policies, leave management, internal code of conducts, and compensation structure.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20958 .

ex:PCF_10422 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Communicate HR strategies""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10422" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.1.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Conveying the strategies of HR function to employees and management. Effectively explain the vision, plans, and anticipated benefits of the HR strategy employees, as well as the public. Develop statements and messages that are easy to read, informative, and relevant to the audience.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20958 .

ex:PCF_10432 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop strategy for HR systems/technologies/tools""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10432" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.1.8" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating a strategy for the use of systems/technologies/tools in operating the HR function. Create a strategy concerning the use and utility of HR support tools and technologies. Decide what specific tools to use and in what quantity. Determine the levels of technology required for the HR management.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20958 .

ex:PCF_20606 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage employer branding""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20606" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.1.9" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating, maintaining and communicating company's reputation and values to keep current employees and attract potential hires.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20958 .

ex:PCF_21432 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage job families and positions""" ;
    ex:pcfID "21432" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.1.10" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Overseeing a group of similar individual or teams with similar education, skills, training, or experience.  """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20958 .

ex:PCF_17045 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop and implement workforce strategy and policies""" ;
    ex:pcfID "17045" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and executing strategies and policies for smooth administration of work force. Determine and gather skill requirements. Plan the requirements for employee resourcing per unit. Create compensation, succession, HR program, and employee diversity plans. Develop and administer policies for HR. Develop benefits for employees. Create models for work force strategies.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17043 .

ex:PCF_10423 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Perform workforce planning""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10423" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Evaluating the current and future skill requirements of the organization with regard to the overall corporate strategy of the organization and market conditions. Identify and establish the minimum skills needed for the requisite HR needs.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17045 .

ex:PCF_10424 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Perform operational workforce planning""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10424" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining the requirements for employees and the need for employee resourcing for each every unit/function. Lay out a plan detailing employee resourcing requirements of individual functions and the organization as a whole.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17045 .

ex:PCF_10425 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop compensation strategy""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10425" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Designing a plan that specifies the combination of wages, salaries, and benefits the employees receive in exchange for work. Define the total amount of compensation, in addition to the manner in which the compensation is paid and the purposes for which employees can receive bonuses, salary increases, and incentives.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17045 .

ex:PCF_10210 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish incentive strategy""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10210" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating a scheme of awards and recognition for sales employees to promote a results-based culture. Create specific incentives to reach desired outcomes, such as landing key clients, growing the customer base, providing exceptional servicing, and increasing profit margins.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10425 .

ex:PCF_10426 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop succession plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10426" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and implementing the plan for continuation of key positions within the organization. Identify internal people with the potential to fill key business leadership positions. Provide critical development experiences to employees who can move into important roles. Engage leaders to support the development of high-potential leaders.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17045 .

ex:PCF_16938 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop high performers/leadership programs""" ;
    ex:pcfID "16938" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating a program that incorporates incentives and compensation put forth by the organization to recognize high performing workers and excellence in leadership.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17045 .

ex:PCF_10427 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop diversity, equity, and inclusion plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10427" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and implementing the plan for ensuring a diverse work force. Develop and hire employees with varying characteristics including, but not limited to, religious and political beliefs, gender, ethnicity, education, socioeconomic background, sexual orientation, and geographic location.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17045 .

ex:PCF_21433 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Implement diversity, equity, and inclusion plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "21433" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Execution of diversity, equity, and inclusion plans within an organization.  Often called a DEI plan.  """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17045 .

ex:PCF_11622 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Design talent development program""" ;
    ex:pcfID "11622" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2.8" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Identifying skills, knowledge, and attributes that need enhancement in order to perform a job. Develop the appropriate training programs. These programs can be computer-based, classroom, or on-the-job training, etc.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17045 .

ex:PCF_11623 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Design talent acquisition program""" ;
    ex:pcfID "11623" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2.9" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Developing a program to entice prospective resources to engage with the organization for a position of employment.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17045 .

ex:PCF_10428 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop other HR programs""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10428" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2.10" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating HR programs and services such as employee engagements programs to promote positive employee behavior. Create a variety of programs and services to support employees' professional and personal needs at work and at home.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17045 .

ex:PCF_10429 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop HR policies""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10429" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2.11" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating rules and regulations that govern the HR function. Develop a policy plan that serves as a guideline for setting rules and regulations that help in achieving the HR goals and objectives.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17045 .

ex:PCF_10430 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Administer HR policies""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10430" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2.12" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Ensuring rules and regulations are followed and are flexible enough to accommodate indispensable deviations.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17045 .

ex:PCF_10431 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Plan employee benefits""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10431" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2.13" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Planning benefits in kind (also called fringe benefits, perquisites, or perks). Include various types of non-wage compensations provided to employees in addition to normal wages or salaries.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17045 .

ex:PCF_10433 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop workforce strategy models""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10433" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2.14" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and implementing models for effectively strategizing the work force of the organization. Develop a model that specifies the organization's overall approach for maximizing the performance of its work force by defining the goals, objectives, and expectations of the work force. Manage all aspects of performance required for the work force to function, including recruitment, selection, retention, and professional development.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17045 .

ex:PCF_20122 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Implement workforce strategy models""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20122" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.2.15" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Implementing models for effectively strategizing the work force of the organization. Carry out all aspects of performance required for the work force to function, including recruitment, selection, retention, and professional development.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17045 .

ex:PCF_10417 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Monitor and update strategy, plans, and policies""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10417" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Supervising the HR strategy, plans, and policies in order to refurbish them whenever needed. Determine the performance of HR plans and policies by measuring the objective achievement rate and its contribution to the overall business strategy. Ensure that information about these plans and strategies is effectively communicated to various stakeholders. Incorporate any suggestions by these stakeholders when revising HR plans and policies.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17043 .

ex:PCF_10434 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Measure realization of objectives""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10434" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining the accomplishment of HR goals and objectives. Evaluate the effectiveness of the HR function by estimating the present rate of achievement of the established objectives. Use metrics to determine if the objectives are being realized. Leverage measures such as turnover, training, return on human capital, costs of labor, and expenses per employee.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10417 .

ex:PCF_10435 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Measure contribution to business strategy""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10435" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining the role of HR function in implementing the organizational strategy. Measure the correlation between the HR performance and the overall business strategy. Calculate the amount of contribution of the HR function to the overall business growth.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10417 .

ex:PCF_10436 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Communicate plans and provide updates to stakeholders""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10436" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Conveying the plans for HR function to stakeholders. Ensure that the HR plans and strategy are effectively communicated to the people who can affect or be affected by the organization's actions, objectives, and policies such as the creditors, shareholders, employees, and suppliers. Provide regular updates to these stakeholders to ensure effective communication.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10417 .

ex:PCF_10438 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Review and revise HR plans""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10438" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.3.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Reassessing the strategies, plans, and policies of the HR function, with the objective of revising them. Revisit the schematic plans for the HR function. Taking stock of any suggestions or feedback from the stakeholders, revamp the blueprint of HR strategies and plans.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10417 .

ex:PCF_17046 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop competency management models""" ;
    ex:pcfID "17046" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.1.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and implementing the tools for managing the competency levels of HR. Design a model for integrating HR planning with business planning. Assess current HR capacity based on the competencies against the capacity needed to achieve the vision, mission, and business goals of the organization. Consider factors such as employee development, career path, compensation policies, and performance management.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17043 .

ex:PCF_10410 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Recruit, source, and select employees""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10410" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining and handling employee requirements. Recruit or source the candidates as per the requirements. Screen and select the most appropriate candidates. Take care of the newly hired and re-hired employees. Maintain records of information for all applicants. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10007 .

ex:PCF_10439 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage employee requisitions""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10439" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Handling the requirements for new employees. Create and open job requisitions by clearly defining the job descriptions. Post these requirements internally and externally, and modify them as appropriate. Manage the dates of the whole requisition process.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10410 .

ex:PCF_10445 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Align staffing plan to work force plan and business unit strategies/resource needs""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10445" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating a correspondence between the plan for hiring new employees and the desired employee requirements. Staff an adequate amount of people with the appropriate skills to effectively accomplish its legislative, regulatory, service, and production requirements.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10439 .

ex:PCF_10447 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop and maintain job descriptions""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10447" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating descriptions for job requisitions. Define the normal components of a job description, such as the overall position description with general areas of responsibility listed, essential functions of the job described with a couple of examples of each, required knowledge, skills, abilities, required education and experience, a description of the physical demands, and a description of the work environment.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10439 .

ex:PCF_10446 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Open job requisitions""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10446" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.1.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Developing specific job requisitions, and ensuring their accessibility. Create and open a job requisition to fill the vacant positions within the organization. Clearly describe the job title, department, fill date, and the requisite skills and qualifications for the job.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10439 .

ex:PCF_10448 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Post job requisitions""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10448" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.1.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Posting and advertising job descriptions. Display open job descriptions internally and externally. Use public portals, online portals, and websites to upload these requisitions in order for applications to be received.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10439 .

ex:PCF_10450 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Modify job requisitions""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10450" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.1.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Making the necessary alterations to job requisitions. Revamp or revise the job requisitions in case a position is filled or is not vacant anymore, as well as in case of any new openings. (It involves Manage the internal/external job posting websites [10449] to make the necessary changes.)""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10439 .

ex:PCF_10451 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Notify hiring manager""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10451" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.1.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Informing and communicating with the hiring manager. Notify the manager responsible for the hiring process in cases of any new position openings or changes.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10439 .

ex:PCF_10452 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage requisition dates""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10452" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.1.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining and managing the dates for the employee requisition process. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10439 .

ex:PCF_10440 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Recruit/Source candidates""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10440" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Recruiting new candidates for deployment across various functional areas inside the organization. Select methods for sourcing new employees. Manage relationships with third-party agencies. Stage recruitment fairs and drives. Manage employee referral programs.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10410 .

ex:PCF_10453 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Determine recruitment methods and channels""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10453" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Defining the methods and channels for recruitments in order to maximize the amount of candidate availability. Use channels such as headhunting, job postings, job portals, networking websites, and media advertising. Choose from the various methods of recruitment such as internal/external third-party sourcing.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10440 .

ex:PCF_10454 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Perform recruiting activities/events""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10454" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Organizing and executing recruiting activities and events. Activities and events include on-campus hiring, refresher courses, information sessions, career fairs, etc. to increase the coverage of the sourcing in order to ensure that the most deserving and appropriate candidates are hired.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10440 .

ex:PCF_10455 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage recruitment vendors""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10455" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Establishing and maintaining relationships with recruitment vendors (suppliers). Create and maintain relationships with third-party agencies such as staffing and firms to expand. Use these relationships to implement the sourcing process effectively.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10440 .

ex:PCF_17047 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage employee referral programs""" ;
    ex:pcfID "17047" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.2.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and managing a recruiting strategy where current employees are rewarded for referring qualified candidates for employment. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10440 .

ex:PCF_17048 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage recruitment channels""" ;
    ex:pcfID "17048" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.2.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Establishing and maintaining channels for recruiting. Extract the best out of every recruitment channel. Manage all the processes related to all the sourcing channels.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10440 .

ex:PCF_20123 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Screen and select candidates""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20123" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Evaluating and selecting potential employees through interviews, tests, etc.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10410 .

ex:PCF_10456 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Identify and deploy candidate selection tools""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10456" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Identifying and implementing tools for the selection of candidates. Recognize candidate selection tools such as screening, telephone interviews, hiring manager interviews, drug testing, and skills assessment. Effectively deploy these tools to check if the candidates fit in the workplace or not, as well as to ensure workplace safety.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20123 .

ex:PCF_10457 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Interview candidates""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10457" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Assessing the candidates by their performance in the interviews. Conduct HR interview, technical interview, hiring manager interview, etc. Understand the mindset of the candidate, and comprehend his/her personal and professional lives.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20123 .

ex:PCF_10458 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Test candidates""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10458" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Examining the candidates through tests. Prepare tools such as aptitude, technical, and grammar tests. Test the skills of the candidate through a written, oral, or computerized test.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20123 .

ex:PCF_10459 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Select and reject candidates""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10459" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.3.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Approving the deserving candidates, and rejecting the others. Examining the performance of candidates. Ensure candidates would fit well with the organization. (Assess performance from Interview candidates [10457] and Test candidates [10458].)""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20123 .

ex:PCF_10443 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage new hire/re-hire""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10443" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and making job offers to the selected candidates. Fairly negotiate the job offers. Agree on terms with the candidate to complete the hiring process.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10410 .

ex:PCF_10463 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Draw up and make offer""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10463" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.4.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Compiling job-related information for the selected candidates in order to make up a job. Include information about the job description, reporting relationship, salary, bonus potential, benefits, and vacation allotment.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10443 .

ex:PCF_10464 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Negotiate offer""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10464" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.4.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Negotiating an offer with selected candidates. Discuss the job offer with the candidate to ensure a mutual understanding. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10443 .

ex:PCF_10465 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Hire candidate""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10465" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.4.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Wrapping up the process for hiring candidates. Agree to all hiring terms and conditions. Have the candidate accept and sign the job offer. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10443 .

ex:PCF_10444 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage applicant information""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10444" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and maintaining a system for managing the information of applicants. Create records for all candidates who apply. Maintain and track information through the use applicant-tracking systems.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10410 .

ex:PCF_10460 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Obtain candidate background information""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10460" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.5.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Conducting a background investigation on the candidates with the objective of looking up and compiling criminal, commercial, and financial records.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10444 .

ex:PCF_10466 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Create applicant record""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10466" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.5.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and documenting the records of all applicants. Manage all individual applicants, including hires and non-hires. Maintain records to avoid any duplication and promote efficiency.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10444 .

ex:PCF_10467 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage/track applicant data""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10467" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.5.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Keeping track of all the information about the candidates who apply for jobs. Use applicant-tracking systems that can be accessed online as a central location and database for recruitment efforts. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10444 .

ex:PCF_20124 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Complete position classification and level of experience""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20124" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.5.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Identifying the requirements for the position to be filled. Determine the experience and skills necessary to perform the tasks outlined.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10467 .

ex:PCF_10468 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Archive and retain records of non-hires""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10468" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.2.5.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Retaining and storing the records of the candidates who were rejected and not hired to ensure future availability in case the need arises. Create a centralized repository of profiles. Label these records in order to readily identify them. Add remarks for any future consideration.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10444 .

ex:PCF_20599 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage employee onboarding, training, and development""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20599" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Assisting employees in developing their capabilities, and providing them counseling services. Handle the orientation and deployment of the employees. Administer the performance of employees. Administer the development and enhancement of the employees. Provide training and development programs for employees.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10007 .

ex:PCF_10469 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage employee orientation and deployment""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10469" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and maintaining various employee on-boarding programs typically known as induction programs in order to ensure that the new employees are effectively introduced to the organization and its existing employees. Examine and evaluate the performance of these induction programs. Execute these programs on the ground level.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20599 .

ex:PCF_10474 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Create/maintain employee onboarding program""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10474" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating and maintaining a mechanism through which new employees acquire the necessary knowledge, skills, and behaviors to become effective organizational members and insiders. Conduct formal meetings, lectures, videos, printed materials, and/or computer-based orientations to introduce newcomers to their new jobs and the organization.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10469 .

ex:PCF_10477 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop employee induction program""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10477" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.1.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Designing a program to systematically introduce newly hired employees to the organizational culture of the company.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10474 .

ex:PCF_10478 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Maintain/Update employee induction program""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10478" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.1.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing the orientation and training of new employees about the organizational culture of the company.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10474 .

ex:PCF_11243 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Evaluate the effectiveness of the employee onboarding program""" ;
    ex:pcfID "11243" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Assessing the performance and effectiveness of employee on-boarding program. Examine the performance of on-boarding program through feedback and reviews from the new employees. Create web and written forms. Obtain information through face-to-face discussions.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10469 .

ex:PCF_17050 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Execute onboarding program""" ;
    ex:pcfID "17050" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.1.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Bringing the employee on-boarding program into effect. Implement Create/Maintain employee on-boarding program [10474]. Conduct training sessions and employee engagement programs.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10469 .

ex:PCF_10470 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage employee performance""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10470" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Defining individual performance objectives. Review performance in order to provide appraisals. Evaluate the efficiency and effectiveness of the current performance program. Update it regularly.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20599 .

ex:PCF_10479 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define employee performance objectives""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10479" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Outlining the objectives for employee performance. Establish key performance objectives and measures such as customer-focus objectives, financially focused objectives, and employee growth objectives.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10470 .

ex:PCF_21434 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Review employee performance""" ;
    ex:pcfID "21434" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Execution of employee reviews/performance on a frequent basis. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10470 .

ex:PCF_21435 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage employee performance""" ;
    ex:pcfID "21435" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Management of reviewing employee performance.  This includes the tools that are used, the frequency of the reviews, and how the reviews are used within the organization. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10470 .

ex:PCF_10481 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Evaluate and review performance program""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10481" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.2.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Assessing and revamping performance programs, including the instruments used to measure employee performance standards. Review and upgrade these performance programs to avoid any deprivations and ensure effectiveness.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10470 .

ex:PCF_10472 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage employee career development""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10472" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Establishing employee development guidelines. Lay out career paths and plans for them. Manage the development of their skills to enhance their skills, ability, and knowledge.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20599 .

ex:PCF_10487 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define employee development guidelines""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10487" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Outlining the guidelines for development of employees. Design development policies and procedures to identify areas of growth for employees, either in their current position or in preparation for future roles. Include topics related to knowledge and skill development.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10472 .

ex:PCF_10488 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop employee career plans and career paths""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10488" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Designing a future career path for the employees that encourages them to explore and gather information. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10472 .

ex:PCF_17051 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage employee skill and competency development""" ;
    ex:pcfID "17051" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.3.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Administering the development of employee skills. Conduct training, coaching and mentoring, job-rotation and cross training, lateral moves, etc.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10472 .

ex:PCF_10473 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop and train employees""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10473" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating a link between employee and organizational development needs. Conduct and manage employee training programs by considering the need and availability of these programs. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20599 .

ex:PCF_10490 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Align employee with organization development needs""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10490" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.4.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Aligning the needs of the employees to development needs.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10473 .

ex:PCF_16940 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Define employee competencies and skills""" ;
    ex:pcfID "16940" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.4.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Defining the skills, knowledge, abilities, and attributes needed to carry out a specific job.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10473 .

ex:PCF_10491 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Align learning programs with competencies and skills""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10491" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.4.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Aligning the learning programs with the core capabilities and competencies of the organization. Contextualize the training programs so that employees can expand their knowledge base and add new skills in line with the core competencies of the organization.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10473 .

ex:PCF_10492 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Establish training needs by analysis of required and available skills""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10492" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.4.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Determining the training necessitated by business processes, using an examination of skill sets that are needed by the organization and those already possessed. Examine the various skills required by individual employees. Design training in light of the availability of resources to provide specific segments of training.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10473 .

ex:PCF_10493 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop, conduct, and manage employee and/or management training programs""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10493" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.4.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating, implementing, and managing the programs for training employees. Create and design sessions on the basis of the needs and the availability of the skills. Conduct the sessions on the ground. Manage all aspects related to the training programs. Consider including literacy training, interpersonal skills training, technical training, problem-solving training, diversity or sensitivity training, etc.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10473 .

ex:PCF_20125 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage examinations and certifications""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20125" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.4.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing identified training programs for employees. Engage with industries to provide certifications, administer certification test, and maintain active certification.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10473 .

ex:PCF_20126 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Liaise with external certification authorities""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20126" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.4.6.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Coordinating with third party certification authorities to provide training and certifications for necessary skills.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20125 .

ex:PCF_20127 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Administer certification tests""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20127" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.4.6.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Providing tests to the workforce that will satisfy completion of certifications.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20125 .

ex:PCF_20128 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Appraise experience qualifications""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20128" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.4.6.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Ascertaining the experience level needed to qualify for a specific job or certification within the organization. Some certificates require practical experience as well as training programs.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20125 .

ex:PCF_20129 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Administer certificate issue and maintenance""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20129" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.4.6.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Administering certificates to all candidates that have successfully met experience qualifications, and passed all tests necessary to obtain the certificate. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20125 .

ex:PCF_21436 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Monitor and evaluate learning programs""" ;
    ex:pcfID "21436" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.3.4.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Oversight of the organization's learning programs.  This process also includes the effectiveness of these programs. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10473 .

ex:PCF_17052 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage employee relations""" ;
    ex:pcfID "17052" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Assisting general management in developing, maintaining, and improving employee relationships. This is accomplished through communication, performance management, processing grievances, and/or dispute. Interpret and convey organizational policies.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10007 .

ex:PCF_10483 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage labor relations""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10483" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.4.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing labor relations, the collective bargaining process, and the relationships between the labor and management. Take care of employee grievances.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17052 .

ex:PCF_10484 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage collective bargaining process""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10484" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.4.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing any negotiations between an employer and a group of employees that determine the conditions of employment. Engage employees to reach agreements in regulating working conditions. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17052 .

ex:PCF_10485 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage labor management partnerships""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10485" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.4.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Handling partnerships between labor and management. Develop a lasting two-way relationship that is beneficial for the labor, management, and the organization.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17052 .

ex:PCF_10531 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage employee grievances""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10531" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.4.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Taking care or resolving any complaint raised by an employee by procedures provided for in a collective agreement, an employment contract, or by other mechanisms established by an employer.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17052 .

ex:PCF_21437 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Monitor legal and regulatory environment""" ;
    ex:pcfID "21437" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.4.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Awareness of the employee legislature that is in place for the organization.  The regulatory environment could include areas, regions, or countries.  """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17052 .

ex:PCF_10412 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Reward and retain employees""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10412" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating frameworks for rewarding and recognizing employees with the objective of retaining them. Create and manage programs for provision of rewards, recognition, and motivation. Manage and administer the benefits for employees. Help assist and retain employees. Administer payroll to employees.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10007 .

ex:PCF_21438 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop and manage reward, recognition, and motivation programs""" ;
    ex:pcfID "21438" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Developing a salary/compensation structure and plan; developing a benefits and reward plan; develop commission plan; performing competitive analyses of benefits and rewards; identifying compensation requirements based on compensation, benefits, and HR policies; administering compensation, commission, and rewards to employees; and rewarding and motivating employees.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10412 .

ex:PCF_10498 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop salary/compensation structure and plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10498" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating the framework for the provision of salary/compensation to employees. Break down the salary structure into different components such as fixed pay, variable pay, bonus, and allowances such medical allowance, and rent allowance, etc. Develop, adjust, and maintain a pay structure.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_21438 .

ex:PCF_10499 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop benefits and rewards plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10499" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.1.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Developing a plan for provision of rewards, commission, and benefits to employees. Plan health benefits, retirement benefits, non-monetary benefits, etc.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_21438 .

ex:PCF_10500 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Perform competitive analysis of benefits and rewards""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10500" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.1.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Analyzing and evaluating the organization's benefits and rewards plan. Compare/Benchmark the benefits and employees plan with other organizations to adhere to industry standard practices.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_21438 .

ex:PCF_10501 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Identify compensation requirements based on financial, benefits, and HR policies""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10501" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.1.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Recognizing the employee requirements for compensation on the basis of the financial, benefits, and HR policies of the organization. Recognize individual compensation requirements regarding the financial policies of the organization. Consider the benefits plan and overall HR policies while selecting compensation requirements.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_21438 .

ex:PCF_10502 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Administer compensation and rewards to employees""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10502" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.1.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing the provision of compensations and rewards to the employees while maintaining consistency with the compensation and benefits plan. Follow the compensation and benefits plan rigorously in order to avoid any discrepancies.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_21438 .

ex:PCF_10503 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Reward and motivate employees""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10503" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.1.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Rewarding and stimulating the performance efforts of employees. Create methods for motivating employees. Spur extrinsic and intrinsic motivation.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_21438 .

ex:PCF_10510 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Review retention and motivation indicators""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10510" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.1.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Reassessing the indicators for retention and motivation of employees. Monitor the indicators that signal the levels of motivation and retention. Regularly update and upgrade indicators to avoid depreciation and ensure high efficiency.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_21438 .

ex:PCF_10511 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Review compensation plan""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10511" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.1.8" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Analyzing existing compensation plans and making changes necessary to continue to retain employees. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_21438 .

ex:PCF_10495 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage and administer benefits""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10495" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing and ensuring benefits enrollment by the employees. Process any benefit claims made by the employees. Balance the estimated amount and entitled amount of benefits.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10412 .

ex:PCF_10504 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Deliver employee benefits program""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10504" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.2.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Implementing the programs that specify employee benefits, other than salary provided, such as those concerning medical care, death, and disability.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10495 .

ex:PCF_10505 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Administer benefit enrollment""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10505" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.2.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Handling the employee enrollment for obtaining benefits. Manage employee enrollment and eligibility. Encourage employees to enroll for benefits.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10495 .

ex:PCF_10506 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Process claims""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10506" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.2.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Processing any formal requests or demands made by the employees claiming that they have earned some benefits. Send the request further up the managerial hierarchy to ensure approval.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10495 .

ex:PCF_10507 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Perform benefit reconciliation""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10507" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.2.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Carrying out reconciliation of benefits delivered to employees. Compare the estimated benefit requirement made by the employee and the actual amount of benefits the employee is entitled to receive.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10495 .

ex:PCF_21439 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage employee assistance and retention""" ;
    ex:pcfID "21439" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing activities centered around delivering programs to support work/life balance for employees; developing family support systems; reviewing retention and motivation indicators; and reviewing compensation plans.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10412 .

ex:PCF_10508 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Deliver programs to support work/life balance for employees""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10508" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.3.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Designing programs that prompt proper balance between work (i.e., career and ambition) and lifestyle (i.e., health, pleasure, leisure, family, and spiritual development/meditation). Account for dependent care, flexible working arrangements, leaves of absence, on-the-job training, etc.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_21439 .

ex:PCF_21440 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage flexible working""" ;
    ex:pcfID "21440" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.3.1.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Task" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creation and execution of a plan that might allow for work from home days, or alternate hours. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10508 .

ex:PCF_10509 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop family support systems""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10509" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.3.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Creating a support structure that aligns with local and federal laws that allow for support for families. This could include things like maternity leave, care for a family member, or in some cases, extended sick leave.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_21439 .

ex:PCF_10497 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Administer payroll""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10497" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.5.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing the sum of all financial records of salaries for an employee, including wages, bonuses, and deductions. Use a payroll management system to deal with the financial aspects of employees' salaries, allowances, deductions, gross pay, net pay, etc. Generate pay slips for a specific period.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10412 .

ex:PCF_10413 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Redeploy and retire employees""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10413" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: ProcessGroup" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing the reassignment and retirement of employees. Manage the process of employee promotion and demotion. Administer separation, retirement, and leaves of absence. Outplace employees. Deploy personnel. Relocate employees in order to manage assignments.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10007 .

ex:PCF_10512 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage promotion and demotion process""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10512" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.6.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Administering the process of promoting and demoting employees. Design a system for advancing or demoting an employee's rank or position. Leverage techniques such as horizontal promotion, vertical promotion, dry promotion, and involuntary/voluntary demotion.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10413 .

ex:PCF_10513 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage separation""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10513" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.6.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing the process of employee separation, including resignations, discharges, and layoffs. Inform the employee of the termination. Complete paperwork for continuation of benefits.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10413 .

ex:PCF_10514 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage retirement""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10514" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.6.3" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing and administering instances where a person stops employment completely.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10413 .

ex:PCF_10515 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage leave of absence""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10515" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.6.4" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing the period of time that an employee must be away from their primary job, while maintaining the status of employee (i.e., paid and unpaid leave of absence but not vacations, holidays, hiatuses, sabbaticals, and work-from-home programs).""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10413 .

ex:PCF_10516 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Develop and implement employee outplacement""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10516" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.6.5" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Helping former employees transition to new jobs or to re-orient themselves in the job market. Deliver help through one-on-one sessions or in a group format. Provide guidance in career evaluation, resume writing, interview preparation, developing networks, and job searching.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10413 .

ex:PCF_20132 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage workforce scheduling""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20132" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.6.6" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Organizing the workforce so that all positions are covered for all shifts with the necessary skilled resources in place. Have a system in place to backfill positions while an employee is on leave.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10413 .

ex:PCF_20133 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Receive required resources/skills and capabilities""" ;
    ex:pcfID "20133" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.6.6.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Obtaining resources necessary to fill a position utilizing specific skills and capabilities.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20132 .

ex:PCF_10517 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage resource deployment""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10517" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.6.6.2" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Allocating employees. Deploy personnel to ensure that the labor of the organization is continuously in an optimal relation to the jobs and organizational structure. """ ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_20132 .

ex:PCF_17055 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Relocate employees and manage assignments""" ;
    ex:pcfID "17055" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.6.7" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Process" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing the relocation of employees in order to carry out assignments. Manage internal business processes to transfer employees, their families, and/or entire departments of a business to a new location.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10413 .

ex:PCF_10520 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
    skos:inScheme apqc:PCF ;
    skos:prefLabel """Manage expatriates""" ;
    ex:pcfID "10520" ;
    ex:hierarchyID "7.6.7.1" ;
    rdfs:comment "APQC level: Activity" ;
    ex:apqcSourceText """Managing foreign resources. Manage employees who are sent to live abroad for a defined time period, as well as non-native employees.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_17055 .

ex:PCF_17056 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
