    ex:apqcSourceText """Making and presenting financial reports to stakeholders. Create annual and quarterly financial statements for reporting purposes. Prepare shareholder reports with details of the profit-and-loss account, balance sheet, and past year's business activities.""" ;
    skos:broader ex:PCF_10750 .

ex:PCF_10843 a owl:NamedIndividual, cco:ont00000853, skos:Concept ;
